   and "free USA shipping". AU-facing price/currency/shipping is unconfirmed —
   Sam to open the link from AU and confirm, then add `price`/`oldPrice`.
   ⚠️ NO ENERGY-SAVINGS CLAIMS anywhere on this page (policy + honesty).
   ========================================================================= */
